      "id": "summary-2",
      "type": "summary",
      "region": "main",
      "order": 2,
      "content": {
        "text": "Former crisis psych admissions coordinator turned product builder. Three years as the first person patients saw during involuntary holds, active detox, and acute psychiatric episodes. Now I build healthcare and AI products. Co-founded Claire Health, a digital healthcare navigation platform that hooks into EDI transmissions to steer employees to lower-cost care. Co-founded Resume Tailor, shipped to 20K users and $48K ARR."
      },
      "tokens": {
        "fontFamily": "Crimson Pro",
        "fontSize": 12,
        "fontWeight": 400,
        "color": "#000000",
        "marginTop": 8,
        "marginBottom": 16
      },
      "decorations": []
    },
    {
      "id": "experience-3",
      "type": "experience",
      "region": "main",
      "order": 3,
      "sectionHeader": "HEALTHCARE & PRODUCT EXPERIENCE",
      "sectionHeaderTokens": {
        "fontFamily": "Crimson Pro",
        "fontSize": 12,
        "fontWeight": 400,
        "color": "#0E539E",
        "marginTop": 12,
        "marginBottom": 6
      },
      "content": {
        "entries": [
          {
            "company": "Claire Health (www.getclairehealth.com)",
            "title": "Co-Founder (Project)",
            "location": "",
            "dateStart": "",
            "dateEnd": "",
            "description": "Built a real-time healthcare navigation platform for self-funded employers that reduces claims costs by steering employees to lower-cost, in-network care.",
            "bullets": [
              [
                {
                  "text": "Platform monitors EDI 270/271 eligibility transmissions and 835/837 claims data to flag high-cost procedures in real time, then redirects care through the employer’s TPA or medical management team to lower-cost sites.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Built the pre-certification intercept workflow: Claire catches scheduled procedures before authorization completes and surfaces lower-cost alternatives via text to employees while they’re still deciding.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Ran a pilot with Meshoppen Stone (220 employees). $1K MRR.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Own product strategy, roadmap, and go-to-market. Work directly with engineering.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ]
            ]
          },
          {
            "company": "Resume Tailor",
            "title": "Co-Founder & Product Manager",
            "location": "",
            "dateStart": "06/2023",
            "dateEnd": "Present",
            "description": "Built an AI job search product from zero to 20K users and $48K ARR. Own product, roadmap, and work directly with engineering.",
            "bullets": [
              [
                {
                  "text": "Ran 50+ user interviews. Key insight: users weren’t avoiding the product because it didn’t work. They were avoiding job searching because rejection hurts. Repositioned the product around that.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Built recruiter outreach after noticing users churned once their resume was done. 25% of actives now use it weekly.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Trial conversion was leaking at 60%. Rebuilt the flow so users could act on insights in one click. Leak dropped to 35%.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Killed mock interviews after 6 weeks. 90% tried it once, almost nobody came back. Moved the team to features that actually retained.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ]
            ]
          },
          {
            "company": "Acadia Healthcare",
            "title": "Admissions Coordinator",
            "location": "",
            "dateStart": "01/2017",
            "dateEnd": "02/2020",
            "description": "First point of contact for patients in psychiatric crisis, like involuntary holds, active detox, and acute behavioral episodes. Worked across inpatient psych, detox, and military units.",
            "bullets": [
              [
                {
                  "text": "Coordinated between patients, families, nurses, and physicians to translate clinical complexity (symptoms, acuity, diagnoses) into fast care placement decisions.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Rebuilt the insurance verification workflow end to end. Admission wait times dropped from 3–4 hours to 45 minutes. Claim approval rates increased.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ],
              [
                {
                  "text": "Managed the full intake process: benefits verification, clinical screening, bed assignment, and family communication across multiple payer types and plan structures.",
                  "bold": false,
                  "italic": false,
                  "underline": false,
                  "color": "#000000"
                }
              ]
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
